I'm home.

00:06.773 --> 00:09.640
Vivian, the birthday boy's here.

00:16.883 --> 00:19.818
Geoffrey? Carlton?

00:19.986 --> 00:21.715
Hilary?

00:21.888 --> 00:25.654
Ashley? Nicky? Anybody?

00:29.295 --> 00:30.990
Will?

